    "## 1. What is (are?) data?\n",
    "\n",
    "A working definition: **data is information recorded through observation or measurement.** That is deliberately broad, because data has taken wildly different physical forms across history:\n",
    "\n",
    "- tally marks carved on bone,\n",
    "- London parish death records,\n",
    "- readings streamed from a wearable fitness device,\n",
    "- every post on a social media platform.\n",
